like":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:22:23.000Z","msg":"天佑國軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天滅中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"915187f67ce2692e5f21d61aed78ea04b8b36e0b","tid":2256433,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dbaedbdc4285592c3fc8e8d25c9645394e98cb8e","tid":2256433,"uid":45977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:22:23.000Z","msg":"天佑國軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n天滅中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:25:28.000Z","msg":"消滅萬惡共匪<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e49d2f1f8187bf177ead3509fa59329b356805","tid":2256433,"uid":288393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T11:31:22.000Z","msg":"支那永遠學唔到自由世界啲文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9f5a48f7f4214349dc187183782bd6ead37f37","tid":2256433,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T15:16:48.000Z","msg":"台灣高調公開「天龍操演」戰機與防砲實彈射擊"},{"pid":"b399e58e82e9a7fb5158c984487e5f25bc1f3ef6","tid":2256433,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T04:22:22.000Z","msg":"台灣高調公開「天龍操演」戰機與防砲實彈射擊"}]}